# Tailwind v4 variable syntax

Use **canonical class names** for theme/CSS variables so the linter (suggestCanonicalClasses) does not flag them.

- **Do:** `border-(--border)`, `bg-(--card)`, `text-(--foreground)`, `bg-(--primary)/10`
- **Don't:** `border-[var(--border)]`, `bg-[var(--card)]`, `text-[var(--foreground)]`

Tailwind v4 treats `(--name)` as shorthand for `var(--name)` in arbitrary values. Use the shorthand everywhere in `className` strings.
